{{italic title}} [[File:Mini World (Japanese magazine).jpg|thumb|300px|issue 78, 2000]] '''''Mini World''''' was an [[English-language education in Japan|English-language Japanese]] [[magazine]] which ran from 1988 to 2001.<ref>Japan English Publications in Print, 1993 - Page 235 " Mini World {MmW} ..."</ref><ref>[http://www.mww.co.jp/ MWW.co.jp] "英文雑誌「ミニワールド」は2001年9月12日発売号をもって休刊いたしました。"</ref> The magazine had a vocabulary level of 2,000 words, equivalent to English standards of the third year of Middle School in Japan.<ref>Shūkan shinchō - 35 (9-16) -1990 Page 102 ミニワールドは、中学 3 年問に習う約 2.000 語の範囲で害かれた英文雑誌です。"</ref>
